1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

Culinara is a next-generation mobile-first web application that reimagines the digital cookbook experience by combining AI-powered recipe assistance with social discovery features. Unlike traditional recipe apps that simply store recipes, Culinara acts as an intelligent cooking companionâ€”helping users generate recipes from available ingredients, understand complex cooking techniques, and adapt recipes to dietary restrictions in real-time.

KEY DIFFERENTIATORS:
â€¢ Native iOS-quality experience delivered through web technologies
â€¢ AI "Sous Chef" that understands context and provides personalized guidance
â€¢ Seamless blend of personal recipe management and community discovery
â€¢ Camera-first interactions for ingredient recognition and recipe digitization
â€¢ Voice-enabled hands-free cooking mode for active kitchen use

TARGET MARKET:
â€¢ Primary: Home cooks aged 25-45 who use AI tools in daily life
â€¢ Secondary: Food enthusiasts who share recipes on social media
â€¢ Tertiary: Dietary-restricted individuals seeking ingredient alternatives

â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
2. PRODUCT VISION & GOALS
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

VISION STATEMENT:
To create a mobile-first web application that feels exactly like a native iOS app, bridging the gap between a recipe storage utility and a social network, using Generative AI to act as a "Sous Chef" that helps users create, understand, and modify recipes on the fly.

PRODUCT GOALS:
1. Eliminate Friction: Reduce recipe discovery and adaptation from 15+ minutes to under 60 seconds
2. Democratize Cooking: Make gourmet techniques accessible through AI-guided explanations
3. Preserve Heritage: Digitize family recipes before they're lost
4. Build Community: Connect home cooks around shared culinary interests
5. Sustainable Cooking: Reduce food waste through intelligent ingredient utilization

SUCCESS CRITERIA (6 MONTHS POST-LAUNCH):
â€¢ 10,000+ active users
â€¢ 50,000+ recipes created or imported
â€¢ 75%+ user retention after 30 days
â€¢ 4.5+ star rating on app stores
â€¢ 5+ AI interactions per user per session

â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
