MARKET OPPORTUNITY:
â€¢ Global recipe app market: $2.5B+ and growing 12% annually
â€¢ 73% of millennials use recipe apps weekly
â€¢ AI cooking assistants are nascent but rapidly growing segment

COMPETITIVE ANALYSIS:

