COMPETITIVE ADVANTAGES:
1. AI-First Approach: Built around AI from day one, not bolted on
2. Multimodal Input: Camera + Voice + Text for maximum flexibility
3. Context-Aware Intelligence: AI understands the entire recipe, not just keywords
4. iOS-Quality UX: Premium mobile experience without app store gatekeeping
5. Privacy-Focused: User owns their data, recipes stay private by default

