KEY FEATURES:
1. Ingredient Checkboxes: Track progress while cooking
2. Substitution Buttons: AI suggests alternatives for any ingredient
3. Inline Chat: Ask questions about specific steps
4. Smart Timers: One-tap timers for each cooking step
5. Scaling: Adjust servings, auto-recalculates all quantities
6. Shopping Mode: Export unchecked ingredients to list

